<item>
            <title>[LU-11982] Incorrect text in lfs migrate help</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11982</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The help for lfs migrate says:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;non-block: do not wait for the operation to return&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;But this is incorrect.&#160; Non-block in fact allows the migrate operation to be interrupted by other operations.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
